->it is called javascript runtime environment

->js se backend nahi ban sakta kyoki js ke pass vo functionalities hi nahi hai jinse backend banta hai.
ek banda hai ryan dahl isne socha js se backend banna chaiye aur ye google chrome ka v8 engine ka code jo ki open source hai uss me chedkaani karta hai, 
kyoki chrome ka v8 engine bana hai c++ mein
fir usne socha ki humein to js mein code krna hai 
fir socha hum js ka code likhenge jo ki wrapper layer of js receive karegi and wo code v8 engine ke c++ modules ke saath ek server create krega

so node.js = js + v8